#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn3.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn3.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. Shackles "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn3.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Mallikāsutta "
msgstr "8. With Queen Mallikā "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.75, sc1
msgctxt "sn3.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.8:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena rājā pasenadi kosalo mallikāya deviyā saddhiṃ uparipāsādavaragato hoti. "
msgstr "Now at that time King Pasenadi of Kosala was upstairs in the stilt longhouse together with Queen Mallikā. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.8:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo mallikaṃ deviṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the king said to the queen, "

msgctxt "sn3.8:1.4"
msgid "“atthi nu kho te, mallike, kocañño attanā piyataro”ti? "
msgstr "“Mallikā, is there anyone more dear to you than yourself?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.8:1.5"
msgid "“Natthi kho me, mahārāja, kocañño attanā piyataro. "
msgstr "“No, great king, there isn’t. "

msgctxt "sn3.8:1.6"
msgid "Tuyhaṃ pana, mahārāja, atthañño koci attanā piyataro”ti? "
msgstr "But is there anyone more dear to you than yourself?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.8:1.7"
msgid "“Mayhampi kho, mallike, natthañño koci attanā piyataro”ti. "
msgstr "“For me also, Mallikā, there’s no-one.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn3.8:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo pāsādā orohitvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho rājā pasenadi kosalo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then King Pasenadi of Kosala came downstairs from the stilt longhouse, went to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and told him what had happened. "

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.2"
msgid "“idhāhaṃ, bhante, mallikāya deviyā saddhiṃ uparipāsādavaragato mallikaṃ deviṃ etadavocaṃ: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.3"
msgid "‘atthi nu kho te, mallike, kocañño attanā piyataro’ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bhante, mallikā devī maṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.5"
msgid "‘natthi kho me, mahārāja, kocañño attanā piyataro. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.6"
msgid "Tuyhaṃ pana, mahārāja, atthañño koci attanā piyataro’ti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.7"
msgid "Evaṃ vuttāhaṃ, bhante, mallikaṃ deviṃ etadavocaṃ: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn3.8:2.8"
msgid "‘mayhampi kho, mallike, natthañño koci attanā piyataro’”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn3.8:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā etamatthaṃ viditvā tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then, knowing the meaning of this, on that occasion the Buddha recited this verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.172, sc4
msgctxt "sn3.8:4.1"
msgid "“Sabbā disā anuparigamma cetasā, "
msgstr "“Having explored every quarter with the mind, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.8:4.2"
msgid "Nevajjhagā piyataramattanā kvaci; "
msgstr "one finds no-one dearer than oneself. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.8:4.3"
msgid "Evaṃ piyo puthu attā paresaṃ, "
msgstr "Likewise for others, each holds themselves dear. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn3.8:4.4"
msgid "Tasmā na hiṃse paramattakāmo”ti. "
msgstr "So one who loves themselves would not harm others.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
